query_total_value

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_total_value -  This method determines the total value of a specified money array.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int query_total_value(mixed mon_array,
string where)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^mon_array%^RESET%^ - the array to find the value of
%^BOLD%^where%^RESET%^ - the money area to get the value in
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the total value as an integer.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/nmoney_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method determines the total value of a specified money array.
A money array consists of pairs of values ({ type, number })
.EP

